Process called "test_discovery_performance" returns List[TestResult]:
    Let results be list containing
    
    Note: Test scanning performance
    Let test1 be run_test("Scanning Performance", test_scanning_performance)
    Append test1 to results
    
    Note: Test metadata extraction performance
